Package: fireData
Title: Connecting R to Google Firebase
Version: 1.16
Authors@R: c(person("Robin", "Kohze", email = "Robin@Kohze.com", role = c("aut", "cre")), 
             person("Paul", "Spende", email = "paul.spende@gmail.com", role = c("aut")))
Author: Robin Kohze [aut, cre],
        Paul Spende [aut]
Description: Provides API access to common features of the Google Firebase realtime database.
    Usecases of firebase are creating user logins with persistent data storage for mobile apps, shiny applications
    or IOT applications. See the fireData github repository for more information.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.3)
